20
00:01:18,810 --> 00:01:19,650
Xia Dashui!

21
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:21,800
You two, get out.

22
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,120
Gouwa?

23
00:01:23,410 --> 00:01:24,680
- Come here.
- You two, get out.

24
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,520
Come here.

25
00:01:26,190 --> 00:01:27,200
- Let's drink.
- Get off!

26
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,640
