34
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,400
If I don't show them who's boss,

35
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,640
how will I control things

36
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,840
- when they act up?
- Xia Dashui,

37
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,360
I never thought

38
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,600
that one day, you'd change

39
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,400
