45
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,640
Look, now I have money,

46
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,240
and women like me.

47
00:02:02,090 --> 00:02:02,930
Even though

48
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,360
