63
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:52,920
The materials are fine.

64
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,960
Gouwa,

65
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,480
you're experienced.

66
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:58,310
How could that happen?

67
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:00,960
Dad,

68
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:03,120
