75
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,240
You're suspended for now.

76
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:24,520
Leave your work to Chongrui.

77
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,080
Dad.

78
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,840
Mr. Zhang.

79
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,760
- Sit.
- Okay.

80
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,140
Mr. Zhang,

81
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,470
