- Good.

83
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:53,920
Thanks to you.

84
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,280
It's my honor.

85
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,080
Mr. Zhang.

86
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:58,300
So,

87
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,320
about

88
