96
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,680
Why does Legal Boy

97
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,360
treat you as a friend?

98
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,200
You even betray your best friend

99
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,280
and you dare to negotiate with me?

100
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,080
You lied to me.

101
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:35,980
That's right.

102
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,640
You liar.

103
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,080
Fine.

104
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:44,000
Very well.

105
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:45,800
Then,

106
00:04:45,910 --> 00:04:47,360
you leave me no choice.

107
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,600
Mr. Zhang.

108
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,160
I'll reveal

109
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,280
what you asked me to do.

110
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,880
If you mess with me,

111
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,240
