112
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,480
Perfect.

113
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,360
You're doomed.

114
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,320
Dashui.

115
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,200
You won't get away with it.

116
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,360
That's good.

117
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,400
I remember

118
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,640
