00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,800
What are you doing here?

127
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,000
To laugh at me?

128
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,880
Dashui.

129
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,800
What's your plan?

130
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:51,960
Where would you go?

131
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,640
I don't know.

132
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,600
But don't worry.

133
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,920
I'll get out of your sight.

134
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,040
Buddy,

135
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:06,600
do you remember?

136
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,120
Six months ago,

137
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:11,680
we worked

138
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:12,800
during the day,

139
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,200
and after work,

140
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,400
we played chess

141
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,600
and chat together.

142
00:07:21,010 --> 00:07:23,030
We argued over a few hundred bucks

143
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,000
with Sun Laoliu,

144
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,560
trying to outsmart each other,

145
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,880
fighting tooth and nail.

146
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:32,320
Life was a bit plain,

147
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,520
but that time

148
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,800
was the happiest of my life.

149
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:41,440
Do you remember?

150
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,250
When I

151
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:45,600
first arrived in this city back then,

152
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,280
if I hadn't met you,

153
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,600
I would've starved to death.

154
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,440
That moment, I knew,

155
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,320
you are my friend for life.

156
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:02,120
I don't care about what the Zhangs gave me.

157
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,040
I only care about my buddies.

158
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:14,400
These are

159
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,280
my savings from the past two years

160
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,240
of working here.

161
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,040
You have to take it.

162
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,360
It's not for you.

163
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,400
It's for your boy.

164
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,600
When you see him,

165
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,360
make sure to tell him

166
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,000
not to be like us.

167
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,640
He must be educated.

168
00:08:38,410 --> 00:08:39,250
Alright.

169
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,640
Gotta go.

170
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,200
Please,

171
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,640
