193
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,440
But,

194
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,320
are you going to mortgage

195
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,880
all our assets?

196
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,400
Jinling,

197
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:47,040
